WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.850 --> 00:00:02.800
What are you doing?

2
00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:05.650
This child just entered the temple a few days ago

3
00:00:05.650 --> 00:00:06.833
Don't know the rules

4
00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:08.983
Pay your money quickly, worship you

5
00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:10.383
What are you looking at?

6
00:00:13.250 --> 00:00:14.700
Go faster

7
00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:18.266
What are you doing here? Don't worry.

8
00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:20.783
Check it later when there are fewer people.

9
00:00:29.650 --> 00:00:31.700
Try scraping the paint on this Buddha statue

10
00:00:36.733 --> 00:00:39.266
Ah, it seems to be real

11
00:00:46.766 --> 00:00:49.750
Ah oh don't be afraid don't be afraid

12
00:00:50.333 --> 00:00:53.383
Hold me tight I'm afraid of this body

13
00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.000
Who received the tears?

14
00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.783
The freshness of this flesh

15
00:00:56.933 --> 00:00:59.300
The time of death should be no more than a day

16
00:01:00.400 --> 00:01:02.083
It turns out that the recently deceased child

17
00:01:02.083 --> 00:01:04.066
All were sent here to be made into statues

18
00:01:05.083 --> 00:01:06.466
What a terrible sacrificial ceremony

19
00:01:06.650 --> 00:01:07.633
I was scared.

20
00:01:07.733 --> 00:01:10.833
Let's go back to Dashun Mansion and ask my father to come over, don't be afraid

21
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:12.133
Can't prove it yet

22
00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:14.150
Why are these children disappearing out of thin air?

23
00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.633
Let's look for it again.

24
00:01:19.333 --> 00:01:20.900
So how do I think it's moving?

